lish domination. The altered short form <i>Bob</i> is very common, but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Robert Ryther was born as the son of Robert Ryther and Anne Tunstall. He had at least 1 son with Lady Margaret Southeby. He died before 1379."},"et":{"–vóór 1379":"–enne 1379","–1379":"–1379","1335–1363":"1335–1363","1350–1426":"1350–1426","1317–1363":"1317–1363","1300–1325":"1300–1325","1426":"1426","after 1325":"pärast 1325","1325":"1325","1335":"1335","1379":"1379","1300":"1300","1363":"1363","1350":"1350","oktober 1363":"oktoober 1363","vóór 1379":"enne 1379","about 1350":"umbes 1350","1317":"1317","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England","Ryther Castle, Ryther, Yorkshire, England":"Ryther, Yorkshire, England"},"fi":{"–vóór 1379":"–ennen vuotta 1379","–1379":"–1379","1335–1363":"1335–1363","1350–1426":"1350–1426","1317–1363":"1317–1363","1300–1325":"1300–1325","1426":"1426","after 1325":"1325 jälkeen","1325":"1325","1335":"1335","1379":"1379","1300":"1300","1363":"1363","1350":"1350","oktober 1363":"lokakuu 1363","vóór 1379":"ennen vuotta 1379","about 1350":"noin 1350","1317":"1317","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England","Ryther Castle, Ryther, Yorkshire, England":"Ryther, Yorkshire, England"},"fr":{"–vóór 1379":"–avant 1379","–1379":"–1379","1335–1363":"1335–1363","1350–1426":"1350–1426","1317–1363":"1317–1363","1300–1325":"1300–1325","1426":"1426","after 1325":"après 1325","1325":"1325","1335":"1335","1379":"1379","1300":"1300","1363":"1363","1350":"1350","oktober 1363":"octobre 1363","vóór 1379":"avant 1379","about 1350":"environ 1350","1317":"1317","Yorkshire, England":"Everwyck, Angleterre","Ryther Castle, Ryther, Yorkshire, England":"Ryther, Everwyck, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Robert Ryther est né, fils de Robert Ryther et Anne Tunstall. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Lady Margaret Southeby. Il est décédé avant 1379."},"de":{"–vó